sources.description:
One Man Against An Entire Army | Northern Shade | Full Action Movie - A battle-hardened army veteran is drawn out of his solitude when his younger brother disappears, only to find out that he has been enticed into a violent extremist militia. In a race against time, the veteran collaborates with a resolute investigator to locate him, maneuvering through a maze of paramilitary training camps, lethal traps, and zealous followers. As the militia gears up to unleash havoc, he must face the soldier he believed he had left in the past, testing his skills, instincts, and moral compass to the utmost in order to rescue his brother and avert a disastrous attack.

Stars: Jesse Gavin, Titania Galliher, Joseph Poliquin
